$BLOCK COMMENT --file copy.3m_datapac.man
NAME
   copy(3f) - [M_datapac:STATISTICS] copy the elements of one vector
   into another vector

SYNOPSIS
      SUBROUTINE COPY(X,N,Y)

DESCRIPTION
   copy(3f) copies the contents of the single precision vector x into
   the single precision vector y.

OPTIONS
    X   description of parameter
    Y   description of parameter

EXAMPLES
  Sample program:

   program demo_copy
   use M_datapac, only : copy
   implicit none
   character(len=*),parameter ::  g='(*(g0,1x))'
   ! call copy(x,y)
   end program demo_copy

